    "library": "A well-stocked library with thousands of technical books and journals.",
    "labs": "Advanced laboratories for all analysis and practical sessions."
  },
  "admissions": {
    "process": "Admissions are conducted through the centralized allotment process by the Government of Kerala. Management seats are filled based on merit.",
